org.odk.collect.android.tasks

Class DownloadFormListTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,java.lang.String,androidx.core.util.Pair<java.util.List<ServerFormDetails>,FormSourceException>>
      • org.odk.collect.android.tasks.DownloadFormListTask

  • public class DownloadFormListTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,java.lang.String,androidx.core.util.Pair<java.util.List<ServerFormDetails>,FormSourceException>>
    Background task for downloading forms from urls or a formlist from a url. We overload this task a bit so that we don't have to keep track of two separate downloading tasks and it simplifies interfaces. If LIST_URL is passed to doInBackground(), we fetch a form list. If a hashmap containing form/url pairs is passed, we download those forms.
